    <h3><b>For Non-Finance Professional Member</b></h3>
    <br><br>
    <p>RichRly offers a platform for non-financial professional to learn about various financial planning strategies through the following ways:</p>
    <ol>
      <li>Learn various financial vehicles and its uses through personal financial stories posted by financial advisors. Personal financial stories detail how a financial advisor helps his/her customer with a particular financial vehicle.</li>
      <li>Learn general financial planning strategy through the blog RichRly provides. Each week, RichRly researches about a specific financial planning topic and post an article to explain various strategies related to the topic.</li>
      <li>Organize your financial planning strategies under your personal financial goals. You can create any financial goal and save the posted financial stories under any particular goal.</li>
      <li>Through profile and posted financial stories, conduct background check on financial advisors to see if any person is fit to be your personal advisor.</li>
      <li>Interact with various financial advisors without direct contact or any commitment.</li>
    </ol>

  </div>
