    <h3><b>For Financial Advisor</b></h3>
    <br><br>
    <p>RichRly offers financial advisors a platform to promote their business through the following ways:</p>
    <ol>
      <li>Advertisement- RichRly offers financial advisors an easy way to advertise for themselves and build credibility with their potential clients. Members can view financial advisors’ profile and learn about their background and experience.</li>
      <li>Showcase your success story- when you post a financial article on RichRly, members can vote up your story if they find it to be helpful. Financial article with the most vote ups will be ranked first. If many people find your article to be helpful, they may contact you and become your client. </li>
      <li>You can use RichRly to conduct market research. You can gather information about member’s financial interest and other profile information to better understand need of your potential clients.</li>
    </ol>
